---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Project.astro";
import Heading from "@/components/ui/Heading.astro";
import Text from "@/components/ui/Text.astro";

const title = "Re:Writing";
const years = "Side Project 2020";
const description = "AI-powered text uniqueness enhancement platform";
---

<Layout {title} {years} {description}>
  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Problem</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]"
    >SEO specialists and content creators struggled with plagiarism detection
    and needed tools to improve text uniqueness for better search rankings.</Text
  >

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Solution</Heading>
  <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]"
    >Built a web platform that analyzed text uniqueness against existing online
    content, provided detailed similarity reports, and offered AI-powered
    rewriting services to improve originality scores.</Text
  >

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Key Features</Heading>
  <ul
    class="list-disc list-inside mb-[1.562rem] space-y-1 text-[var(--color-text)]"
  >
    <li>Free uniqueness analysis with competitor content detection</li>
    <li>Visual similarity breakdown with percentage scores</li>
    <li>Paid rewriting service increasing uniqueness by 50%+ on average</li>
    <li>Before/after comparison showing improvement metrics</li>
  </ul>

  <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">Outcome</Heading>
  <Text
    >Developed 5 years before mainstream AI adoption, using early natural
    language processing techniques to compete with established plagiarism
    detection services. Successfully served paying customers in the SEO
    industry. Project discontinued due to high operational costs relative to
    content quality limitations of pre-transformer AI models.</Text
  >
</Layout>
